{"tid":1801749,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【台灣選戰】韓國瑜義賣原味Jacket 超級韓粉$25萬投得","createTime":"2019-12-29T01:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T01:36:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edc6cc55d015e6b507d2b2b7707d7e3142aa662d","tid":1801749,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"62歲大叔的原味Jacket，都值20萬港元！？進入台灣大選倒數最後兩周，國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜今日義賣他出席公開活動經常穿着的Iron Han Jacket「鋼鐵H夾克」，現場氣氛熱烈，有韓國瑜簽名、編號2020的鋼鐵H夾克，最終以80萬元新台幣（下同，約20.7萬港元）賣出；韓國瑜最後也脫下身上的原味「鋼鐵H夾克」，支持者以100萬元（約25.8萬港元）投得，義賣所得將全數捐作公益。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，韓國瑜之所以今日大搞義賣活動，主要是因為近日不斷有韓粉查問，他出席競選活動時經常穿着的一件深藍色夾克在哪處售賣。而夾克是他的競選制服，並取名為Iron Han Jacket，是由韓國瑜朋友設計。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜競選辦公室選見夾克受到不少韓粉喜愛，於是今日在「鋼鐵夾克」愛心拍賣會，準備1,000件夾克義賣，每件2,500元（約646港元）；而有韓國瑜簽名的一件更以5,200元起標（約1,345港元），韓國瑜親自拍賣5件夾克，義賣所得會全數捐給慈善團體。<br />\n<br />\n今天一早，就有鋼鐵韓粉在現場排隊，PTT名人「四叉貓」劉宇也排隊拿號碼牌，搶到361號。由於反應熱烈，韓國瑜親筆簽名的夾克增加至20件，每件叫價都破20萬元（約5.1萬港元）。而韓國瑜一現身會場，首拍出第一件夾克外套就以53萬元（約13.7萬港元）成交，另一件編號2020的鋼鐵H夾克，更以80萬元成功出售。而活動去到最後，韓國瑜更加碼將身上穿着的原味外套拍賣，最終以100萬元成交。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/29/091834_8783b70913e0ce291f08ffc60e2043c4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F29%2F091834_8783b70913e0ce291f08ffc60e2043c4.jpeg&h=74f80343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國瑜（中間）的競逐夾克公開義賣，他還即場除下身上的一件，即場拍賣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191228/60426416?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60426416%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNaDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=bd6c52fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60426416%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=bc1861f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191228/60426416?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"fc0ce3aed7eecf7958ae5b3c1f77905e5de076e3","tid":1801749,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中聯辦千萬書法"},{"pid":"f769bd1110ca01952659ff6632ad711199741e73","tid":1801749,"uid":2900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得件嘢係成陣酸叔呀伯味 勁多頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底韓國魚嘅政治魅力係喺邊度"},{"pid":"4dc76b91395744cff6a3ccc0d54559a1b16446d5","tid":1801749,"uid":19372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0ce3aed7eecf7958ae5b3c1f77905e5de076e3","tid":1801749,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中聯辦千萬書法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:34:45.000Z","msg":"國台辦呀<br />\n巧立名目捐款，內裡咪又政治獻金"},{"pid":"ce3347121e00b495e82136d2622755f2d89f40f0","tid":1801749,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"個陣佬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}